{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2021-01-30-random-music-generators-news/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"scraggo.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ef97f645-0325-5bf1-806d-ba14610e6780","excerpt":"New in 1.3.1 This month, I released a big new feature that’s been requested often. You can now specify a custom note collection to create random melodies. Check…","html":"<h2>New in 1.3.1</h2>\n<p>This month, I released a big new feature that’s been requested often. You can now <em>specify a custom note collection</em> to create random melodies. <a href=\"https://random-music-generators.herokuapp.com/melody\">Check it out!</a></p>\n<p>Note: This feature is available to use if you create an account.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/21002ebfc519b4cf5cab11a2f92fcccd/b3d4b/custom-pitch-collection.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.63793103448275%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Custom pitch collection\"\n        title=\"Custom pitch collection\"\n        src=\"/static/21002ebfc519b4cf5cab11a2f92fcccd/799d3/custom-pitch-collection.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/21002ebfc519b4cf5cab11a2f92fcccd/00d96/custom-pitch-collection.png 148w,\n/static/21002ebfc519b4cf5cab11a2f92fcccd/0b23c/custom-pitch-collection.png 295w,\n/static/21002ebfc519b4cf5cab11a2f92fcccd/799d3/custom-pitch-collection.png 590w,\n/static/21002ebfc519b4cf5cab11a2f92fcccd/2a3d6/custom-pitch-collection.png 885w,\n/static/21002ebfc519b4cf5cab11a2f92fcccd/b3d4b/custom-pitch-collection.png 928w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Part of the impetus to provide this feature was to aid in neuroscience research. Having the ability to create melodies with specific pitches will allow researchers to study <code class=\"language-text\">tonal memory</code> (working auditory memory for pitches) and how many notes of a specific type will saturate it. How cool is that?!</p>\n<p>I also updated the display of the chord progression playback so it’s easier to tell where you are in the progression:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2873a7b079e374b3d236a97cd089b07f/767e4/chord-playback.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.02189781021898%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Chord display\"\n        title=\"Chord display\"\n        src=\"/static/2873a7b079e374b3d236a97cd089b07f/799d3/chord-playback.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2873a7b079e374b3d236a97cd089b07f/00d96/chord-playback.png 148w,\n/static/2873a7b079e374b3d236a97cd089b07f/0b23c/chord-playback.png 295w,\n/static/2873a7b079e374b3d236a97cd089b07f/799d3/chord-playback.png 590w,\n/static/2873a7b079e374b3d236a97cd089b07f/2a3d6/chord-playback.png 885w,\n/static/2873a7b079e374b3d236a97cd089b07f/767e4/chord-playback.png 1096w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>In addition to these new features, there were a couple of bug fixes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>In the Melody > Varied Rhythm section, if you entered No. Measures more than 1, it was just repeating the first measure.</li>\n<li>Melody Presets were failing to load</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Stats</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Over 101,000 people have used the app since September 2019</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Check it out!</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://random-music-generators.herokuapp.com/\">Random Music Generators - Heroku</a></p>\n<h2>Suggest features</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/contact\">Contact me</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/2021-01-30-random-music-generators-news/"},"frontmatter":{"author":"Dave Cohen","categories":["tech"],"date":"January 30, 2021","description":null,"tags":["random music generators"],"title":"Random Music Generators News 2021-01-30"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2021-01-30-random-music-generators-news/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech-career-resources/"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["career"],"title":"Are You Ready to be a Professional Software Engineer?","type":"post"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/design-patterns-intro/"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["design patterns"],"title":"Introduction to Design Patterns: Why they're worth learning","type":"post"}}}}}